variables.name: sessionCreatedTimeUs
variables.comment: System time of when the session is created.

variables.name: sessionFinishedTimeUs
variables.comment: System time of when the session is finished.

variables.name: totalProcessingTimeUs
variables.comment: Total time spend on transcoding, exclude the time in pause.

variables.name: totalTimeUs
variables.comment:
* Total time spend on handling the session, include the time in pause.
   * The totaltimeUs is actually the same as sessionFinishedTimeUs - sessionCreatedTimeUs.
